Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Tony Parker?

Tony Parker is 41 years old.

Where was Tony Parker born?

Tony Parker was born in Bruges, Belgium.

When was Tony Parker born?

Tony Parker was born on May 17, 1982.

How tall is Tony Parker?

Tony Parker is 6-2 (188 cm) tall.

How much did Tony Parker weigh when playing?

Tony Parker weighed 185 lbs (83 kg) when playing.

Is Tony Parker in the Hall of Fame?

Tony Parker was inducted to the Hall of Fame as a Player in 2023 (Full List) .

When was Tony Parker drafted?

Tony Parker was drafted by San Antonio Spurs, 1st round (28th pick, 28th overall), 2001 NBA Draft.

What position did Tony Parker play?

Point Guard.

When did Tony Parker retire?

Tony Parker last played in 2019.

What is Tony Parker's net worth?

Tony Parker made at least $168,282,460 playing professional basketball.

How much did Tony Parker make?

Tony Parker made $15,453,126 in 2018.

What did Tony Parker average?

Tony Parker averaged 15.5 points, 2.7 rebounds, and 5.6 assists per game.

How many rings does Tony Parker have?

Tony Parker won 4 championships.

What is Tony Parker's Twitter account?

Tony Parker is on Twitter at tonyparker.

What are Tony Parker's nicknames?

T.P., Fiery Francophile, Parisian Torpedo are nicknames for Tony Parker.
